12:34.921 --> 12:36.252
Your call.

13:01.614 --> 13:03.275
I'll take care of it.

13:23.469 --> 13:26.438
Mrs Ganush. I'm sorry, Mrs Ganush,

13:26.539 --> 13:29.303
but another extension on the loan
is out of the question.

13:29.375 --> 13:31.866
-What?
-I would like to help, but it is in the bank's...

13:31.978 --> 13:36.381
