Where will I live?

13:37.717 --> 13:40.447
You list your granddaughter as a reference.
Maybe you could stay with her.

13:40.553 --> 13:42.145
I would not burden her.

13:43.656 --> 13:46.318
And there are several fine assisted
living facilities for the elderly...

13:46.392 --> 13:51.227
