14:31.771 --> 14:34.103
-I humble myself before you.
-Mrs Ganush. Mrs Ganush, please.

14:34.207 --> 14:36.869
-Please stand up.
-I, Sylvia Ganush, beg.

14:36.943 --> 14:39.935
