you lose your house.

23:12.391 --> 23:15.053
What does this woman expect?
It's not your fault.

23:15.127 --> 23:17.687
You can't beat yourself up over it.

23:24.637 --> 23:27.401
CLAY: I mean, what'd she expect?
It's not your fault.

23:27.473 --> 23:30.636
