or may not have been able to do,

23:30.910 --> 23:33.538
that's still no justification for her...

23:41.820 --> 23:44.050
What is it? What's wrong?

23:44.590 --> 23:47.559
-Did you hear that?
-What?

23:47.993 --> 23:49.483
Really? You didn't?

23:50.996 --> 23:52.657
No. What?

23:57.002 --> 24:00.165
I know this is gonna sound weird,
but I wanna get my fortune read.

24:01.240 --> 24:05.176
(LAUGHS) Now? Are you kidding?

24:06.845 --> 24:09.678
Come on, Chris. I'll read your fortune for you.

24:10.182 --> 24:12.173
In the near future,
we are gonna get in the car,

24:12.284 --> 24:15.185
-go home and relax.
-Clay, I really want to do this.

24:15.287 --> 24:18.017
