which is a weird little dried monkey head.

24:48.887 --> 24:51.048
Wait, no, never mind, he's got one.

24:53.726 --> 24:56.058
I am Rham Jas, seer.

24:56.895 --> 25:01.730
-I'm Christine and this is Clay.
-But you probably already knew that, right?

25:03.402 --> 25:06.337
-Just kidding.
-How can I help you?

25:06.405 --> 25:10.000
I would like to have my fortune read.
Can you do that?

25:10.075 --> 25:13.135
I have the ability to see certain energies.

25:13.245 --> 25:16.840
Sometimes these energies
are a foretoken of things to come.

25:16.915 --> 25:18.177
$60, please.

25:18.250 --> 25:20.013
-Seriously?
-Yes.

25:20.085 --> 25:23.748
Sixty... Doesn't that seem a little
steep for this sort of thing?

25:23.856 --> 25:28.657
-If you're not serious, please go.
-All right. Come on, Chris.

25:28.761 --> 25:31.321
Wait, wait! I'll... I'll pay.

25:31.430 --> 25:34.593
No, you know what?
You know what? I got it. I got it.

25:35.267 --> 25:39.431
-There you go.
-Platinum card. Very good.

25:45.544 --> 25:46.772
CHRISTINE: Thank you.

25:47.346 --> 25:48.745
-Here, here, baby.
-Thanks.

25:48.847 --> 25:50.041
Sure.

25:52.451 --> 25:55.215
Uh-uh. Please.

25:56.121 --> 25:57.110
Okay.

25:57.856 --> 26:00.723
So, you wish to know
something of your destiny.

26:00.793 --> 26:01.953
-Yes.
-Very good.

26:02.061 --> 26:03.551
Let's see what the fates have in store.

26:03.629 --> 26:05.893
